<h2>Reset Your Password</h2>
<p>Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
<p>We received a request to reset the password for your account. Click the button below to set a new password.</p>

<p style="text-align:center;">
  <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="btn">Reset My Password →</a>
</p>

<div class="warning-box">
  <p>⏱ <strong>This link expires in {{expiresIn}} minutes.</strong> After that, you'll need to request a new reset link.</p>
</div>

<div class="divider"></div>
<p style="font-size:13px; color:#999;">If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email — your password will remain unchanged. For security, this link can only be used once.</p>

<p style="font-size:13px; color:#999;">Can't click the button? Copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
<p style="font-size:12px; color:#667eea; word-break:break-all;">{{resetLink}}</p>
